title: I AM MOTHER Ending Explained! Netflix 2019
author: Think Story
comment: Ughh, I'm such an idiot and missed the perfect opportunity to end the video with "Mommy loves you very much!"
The daughter becoming the mother is another phase of experiment. The mother robot will still observe her from afar.

Thanos: "I want to wipe out half of humanity."

Mother: "Lol, that's cute."
I'm not gonna lie, I really do hope there's a part 2 to this movie haha
The actress who played daughter did an incredible job
